#

Smoked Gouda Mac and Cheese

$18.5
750 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Comfort FoodAmerican

Tags:

CheeseBaconPasta

Description

A creamy, smoky mac and cheese with crunchy applewood bacon.

Ingredients

  • Elbow macaroni: 1 pound
  • Unsalted butter: 4 tablespoons
  • All-purpose flour: 1/4 cup
  • Whole milk: 4 cups
  • Smoked Gouda cheese, shredded: 3 cups
  • Sharp cheddar cheese, shredded: 1 cup
  • Applewood smoked bacon, cooked and crumbled: 8 slices
  • Salt: 1 teaspoon
  • Black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • Paprika: 1/4 teaspoon
